data.description: Good bones! Investor Alert!!This well built one story home just needs a little elbow grease and some imagination to make it shine again. This home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Wood burning fireplace in living room. Kitchen has breakfast bar and pantry. Large two car garage and fenced yard. 3 minutes from shopping, golf course and marina. 10 minutes to the Hood Canal Bridge and Kitsap Peninsula. Opportunity knocks with this one! This is a Short Sale.
